アンドロメダを中心とする波動砲艦隊と、バルゼー率いるガトランティスの大艦隊が、太陽圏で激突する。\r\n地球の、宇宙の命運を決する戦いの行方は──!?"},{"id":839523,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/839523","type":0,"sort":18,"name":"ヤマト絶体絶命・悪魔の選択再び","duration":"","airdate":"2018-05-25","comment":0,"desc":"脚本：福井晴敏・岡秀樹／絵コンテ：麻宮騎亜／演出：小谷野竜成／作画監督：結城信輝\r\n\r\n木星に匹敵する大きさを誇る白色彗星。いま、その内奥に眠る都市帝国が、ついにその全貌を現す。\r\nそして再び突きつけられるズォーダーの“悪魔の選択”。\r\nラスト、かつてない衝撃がヤマトを襲う──。"}],"staff":[{"id":5772,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/df/ae/5772_prsn_N71Ni.jpg","name":"S.E.N.S.","desc":"主题歌作曲"},{"id":5772,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/df/ae/5772_prsn_N71Ni.jpg","name":"S.E.N.S.","desc":"主题歌作词"},{"id":3502,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/83/39/3502_prsn_S3uWc.jpg","name":"バンダイナムコエンターテインメント","desc":"製作"},{"id":551,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/86/6b/551_prsn_q7EkK.jpg","name":"XEBEC","desc":"动画制作"},{"id":7587,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5e/4d/7587_prsn_KGneK.jpg","name":"BANPRESTO","desc":"製作"},{"id":551,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/86/6b/551_prsn_q7EkK.jpg","name":"XEBEC","desc":"製作"},{"id":2369,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a0/6b/2369_prsn_SxVz3.jpg","name":"谷岡善王","desc":"美术监督"},{"id":1433,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2a/70/1433_prsn_Jw0wX.jpg","name":"松竹","desc":"製作"},{"id":32509,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/be/09/32509_prsn_00Ksk.jpg","name":"バンダイナムコアーツ","desc":"製作"},{"id":3141,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/dd/7b/3141_prsn_DSL2c.jpg","name":"アサツー ディ・ケイ","desc":"製作"},{"id":18776,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/ad/18776_prsn_M5a5K.jpg","name":"バンダイ","desc":"製作"},{"id":1285,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6b/d1/1285_prsn_WaFr3.jpg","name":"東北新社","desc":"音响"},{"id":32509,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/be/09/32509_prsn_00Ksk.jpg","name":"バンダイナムコアーツ","desc":"音乐制作"},{"id":20775,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/54/7d/20775_prsn_oGq14.jpg","name":"サブリメイション","desc":"3DCG"},{"id":1286,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/da/ac/1286_prsn_866WJ.jpg","name":"Production I.G","desc":"制作助手"},{"id":166,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a4/04/166_prsn_EYy1Y.jpg